1st Photography Contest in our Barangay:
-OPEN CATEGORY_
Mechanics and Criteria:
1. First 15 participants will be entertained and to exhibit one(1) photo taken on (October 6, 2018)-Orientation@ Barangay Alapang Hall/Office(1-2 slots)/representative/s per school @ 8am.
2. Participants must register and report at the designated briefing room 1 hour before the departure to the destination(the destination refers to the venue where the participants will take pictures)
3. The photo must be raw, unedited and in full color, glossy mate is allowed.
6. The photo must be relevant to the theme. Theme: Alapang at its Finest: The Hidden Views of Brgy. Alapang
7. The photographer must write a brief and concise caption of the picture 
8. Participants should be at the meeting place/venue-30 minutes before the competition proper. **LATE participants/competitors mean DISQUALIFICATION from the competition.
October 6,2018/Orientation/Briefing 8:00am,
Picture Taking 8:30am-4:45pm, Submission of the output (FLASHDRIVE/USB ONLY).-5:00pm
9. The registration fee is one hundred pesos (PHP 100.00) which will cover (1) snack, certificate of attendance, printing of your photo.
Criteria: 
PHOTO “FIT” AND RELEVANCE TO CATEGORY - 20 pts 
(the photo meets the criteria of the category)
COMPOSITION - 20 pts 
(focus is well presented in the photo)
CREATIVITY - 20 pts 
(the photo in focus, lighting in balance/depth of field considered/used/shutter speed varied or adjusted to be appropriate for the photo)
OVER-ALL IMPRESSION - 20 pts 
(the photo should able to grab the viewer’s attention and hold its ”WOW” factor or special effects)
TOTAL POINTS = 100 PTS

1st Place
2nd Place
3rd Place
***With CASH Prize +certificate of Recognition
